{"hash":"2d548d3e1282098816694257d5731ee287bcb6e0","data":{"post":{"title":"How to set up Tailwind CSS with Gridsome","path":"/article/how-to-set-up-tailwind-css-with-gridsome/","date":"17 Oct 2022","timeToRead":2,"content":"<p>Using Tailwind CSS with Gridsome framework is relatively not easy as using it with other Jamstack frameworks such as Gatsby and many others.</p>\n<br>\n<p>So, in this guide, I will be showing you how to add and style your Gridsome project with Tailwind CSS in a simple approach. </p>\n<br>\n<p>We will also be adding <strong>Autoprefixer</strong> for cross-browser compatibility and <strong>PurgeCSS</strong> to reduce stylesheets size in an attempt to increase website load speed.</p>\n<br>\n<p>The first thing to do is install <strong>Tailwind CSS</strong>, <strong>PostCSS-PurgeCSS</strong> and <strong>Autoprefixer</strong>. To save time, we will be doing this in one go, run the following command with your terminal: <br><br/></p>\n<pre class=\"shiki\" style=\"background-color: #2e3440ff\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\">Yarn: yarn add tailwindcss@npm:@tailwindcss/postcss</span><span style=\"color: #B48EAD\">7</span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\">-compat @tailwindcss/postcss</span><span style=\"color: #B48EAD\">7</span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\">-compat postcss@^</span><span style=\"color: #B48EAD\">7</span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\"> autoprefixer@^</span><span style=\"color: #B48EAD\">9</span></span></code></pre>\n<br>\n<pre class=\"shiki\" style=\"background-color: #2e3440ff\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\">NPM: npm install tailwindcss@npm:@tailwindcss/postcss</span><span style=\"color: #B48EAD\">7</span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\">-compat @tailwindcss/postcss</span><span style=\"color: #B48EAD\">7</span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\">-compat postcss@^</span><span style=\"color: #B48EAD\">7</span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\"> autoprefixer@^</span><span style=\"color: #B48EAD\">9</span></span></code></pre>\n<br>\n<p>After a successful installation, create a folder named <strong>css</strong> in your <strong>/src</strong> directory and also make a <strong>styles.css</strong> file under the <strong>css</strong> folder. Then add the following content, it consists of tailwind base, components and utilities classes:</p>\n<br>\n<pre class=\"shiki\" style=\"background-color: #2e3440ff\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #81A1C1\">@tailwind</span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\"> base</span><span style=\"color: #81A1C1\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #81A1C1\">@tailwind</span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\"> components</span><span style=\"color: #81A1C1\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #81A1C1\">@tailwind</span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\"> utilities</span><span style=\"color: #81A1C1\">;</span></span></code></pre>\n<br>\n<p>Now import the <strong>styles.css</strong> file in your <strong>main.js</strong> file:</p>\n<br>\n<pre class=\"shiki\" style=\"background-color: #2e3440ff\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #81A1C1\">import</span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">&#39;</span><span style=\"color: #A3BE8C\">./css/main.css</span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">&#39;</span></span></code></pre>\n<br>\n<p>We also need to generate a configuration file for Tailwind, run <strong>npx tailwind init</strong> and a <strong>tailwind.config.js</strong> file will be generated in our root directory. Paste in the following config settings:</p>\n<br>\n<pre class=\"shiki\" style=\"background-color: #2e3440ff\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #8FBCBB\">module</span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">.</span><span style=\"color: #8FBCBB\">exports</span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #81A1C1\">=</span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">{</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\">  </span><span style=\"color: #88C0D0\">purge</span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">:</span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">{</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\">    </span><span style=\"color: #88C0D0\">content</span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">:</span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\"> [</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\">      </span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">&#39;</span><span style=\"color: #A3BE8C\">./src/**/*.vue</span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">&#39;</span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">,</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\">      </span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">&#39;</span><span style=\"color: #A3BE8C\">./src/**/*.js</span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">&#39;</span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">,</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\">      </span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">&#39;</span><span style=\"color: #A3BE8C\">./src/**/*.jsx</span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">&#39;</span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">,</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\">      </span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">&#39;</span><span style=\"color: #A3BE8C\">./src/**/*.html</span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">&#39;</span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">,</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\">      </span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">&#39;</span><span style=\"color: #A3BE8C\">./src/**/*.pug</span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">&#39;</span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">,</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\">      </span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">&#39;</span><span style=\"color: #A3BE8C\">./src/**/*.md</span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">&#39;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\">    ]</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\">  </span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">},</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\">  </span><span style=\"color: #88C0D0\">theme</span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">:</span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">{</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\">    </span><span style=\"color: #88C0D0\">extend</span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">:</span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">{},</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\">  </span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">},</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\">  </span><span style=\"color: #88C0D0\">variants</span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">:</span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">{},</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\">  </span><span style=\"color: #88C0D0\">plugins</span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">:</span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\"> []</span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">,</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">}</span></span></code></pre>\n<br>\n<p>Finally, we have to tell Gridsome to add Tailwind, PurgeCSS and Autoprefixer in our project. Paste the following config settings inside the <strong>gridsome.config.js</strong> file:</p>\n<br>\n<pre class=\"shiki\" style=\"background-color: #2e3440ff\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #81A1C1\">const</span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9\">tailwind</span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #81A1C1\">=</span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #88C0D0\">require</span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\">(</span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">&#39;</span><span style=\"color: #A3BE8C\">tailwindcss</span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">&#39;</span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\">)</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #81A1C1\">const</span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9\">autoprefixer</span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #81A1C1\">=</span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #88C0D0\">require</span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\">(</span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">&#39;</span><span style=\"color: #A3BE8C\">autoprefixer</span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">&#39;</span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\">)</span></span>\n\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #8FBCBB\">module</span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">.</span><span style=\"color: #8FBCBB\">exports</span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #81A1C1\">=</span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">{</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\">  </span><span style=\"color: #88C0D0\">siteName</span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">:</span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">&#39;</span><span style=\"color: #A3BE8C\">Yoursitename</span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">&#39;</span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">,</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\">  </span><span style=\"color: #88C0D0\">plugins</span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">:</span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\"> [</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\">    </span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">{</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\">      </span><span style=\"color: #88C0D0\">use</span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">:</span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">&#39;</span><span style=\"color: #A3BE8C\">@gridsome/source-filesystem</span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">&#39;</span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">,</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\">      </span><span style=\"color: #88C0D0\">options</span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">:</span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">{</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\">        </span><span style=\"color: #88C0D0\">path</span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">:</span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">&#39;</span><span style=\"color: #A3BE8C\">blog/**/*.md</span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">&#39;</span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">,</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\">        </span><span style=\"color: #88C0D0\">typeName</span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">:</span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">&#39;</span><span style=\"color: #A3BE8C\">Post</span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">&#39;</span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">,</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\">        </span><span style=\"color: #88C0D0\">refs</span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">:</span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">{</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\">          </span><span style=\"color: #88C0D0\">tags</span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">:</span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">{</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\">            </span><span style=\"color: #88C0D0\">typeName</span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">:</span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">&#39;</span><span style=\"color: #A3BE8C\">Tag</span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">&#39;</span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">,</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\">            </span><span style=\"color: #88C0D0\">create</span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">:</span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #81A1C1\">true</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\">          </span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">},</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\">        </span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">},</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\">      </span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">}</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\">    </span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">}</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\">  ]</span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">,</span></span>\n\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\">  </span><span style=\"color: #88C0D0\">templates</span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">:</span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">{</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\">    </span><span style=\"color: #88C0D0\">Tag</span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">:</span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">&#39;</span><span style=\"color: #A3BE8C\">/tag/:id</span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">&#39;</span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">,</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\">    </span><span style=\"color: #88C0D0\">Post</span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">:</span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">&#39;</span><span style=\"color: #A3BE8C\">/blog/:path</span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">&#39;</span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">,</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\">  </span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">},</span></span>\n\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\">  </span><span style=\"color: #88C0D0\">css</span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">:</span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">{</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\">    </span><span style=\"color: #88C0D0\">loaderOptions</span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">:</span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">{</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\">      </span><span style=\"color: #88C0D0\">postcss</span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">:</span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">{</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\">        </span><span style=\"color: #88C0D0\">plugins</span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">:</span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\"> [</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\">          </span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9\">tailwind</span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">,</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\">          </span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9\">autoprefixer</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\">        ]</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\">      </span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">}</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\">    </span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">}</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\">  </span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">}</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">}</span></span></code></pre>\n<br>\n<p>To verify whether everything is working perfectly or not, restart your project development server by running <strong>gridsome develop</strong> and add these text styles inside a component:</p>\n<br>\n<pre class=\"shiki\" style=\"background-color: #2e3440ff\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #81A1C1\">&lt;h2</span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #8FBCBB\">class</span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">=</span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #A3BE8C\">text-2xl text-center</span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #81A1C1\">&gt;</span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\">Tailwind configuration is successful</span><span style=\"color: #81A1C1\">&lt;/h2&gt;</span></span></code></pre>\n<br>\n<p>Everything should be displaying fine now, which brings us to the end of this guide. If you have any question, comment down below ðŸ‘‡.</p>\n","tags":[{"id":"tailwind","title":"tailwind","path":"/tag/tailwind/"}]}},"context":{}}